text: Andrzej Potocki (1618-1663) was a Polish noble. He was Obozny of the Crown since 1665, voivode of Bracław Voivodeship since 1662 and starost of Winnica. Andrzej Potocki married his cousin Wiktoria Elżbieta Potocka. Category:1618 births Category:1663 deaths Andrzej Potocki
title: Andrzej Potocki (1618–1663)
